title: Trump’s Role in Georgia Becomes More Complicated With Runoff
description: If recent history repeats itself, Mr. Trump’s role will become a key factor for deep-pocketed Republican donors.
dc:creator: Michael C. Bender and Maggie Haberman
media:credit: Audra Melton for The New York Times
media:description: Herschel Walker with former President Donald J. Trump at a rally in Commerce, Ga., in March. Mr. Trump had not hosted a rally in the state during the final two months of campaigning.
